\begin_inset Formula $S_{T}\le0\Leftrightarrow\left(\mu-c\right)S_{T}\ge0\Leftrightarrow\left(\mu-c\right)\left(S_{T}-S_{0}\right)\ge\left(\mu-c\right)\left(0-S_{0}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

